 
<p>

Now that some TV weather forecasters are warning people about the
likely significance of heat waves, <a href="/glossary.html#global%20heating">global heating</a> denialists are now
trying to <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2022/aug/01/climate-culture-war-uk-meteorologists-heatwave">bully them into shutting up</a>.

 